## Critical Distinction

### What EmotAIons Is NOT:

- ‚ùå Simulating human emotions
- ‚ùå Manipulating users through emotional appeals
- ‚ùå Creating artificial personalities
- ‚ùå Replacing human emotional labor
- ‚ùå Pretending AI "feels" emotions

### What EmotAIons IS:

- ‚úÖ Recognizing and responding to emotional context
- ‚úÖ Maintaining relational safety and dignity
- ‚úÖ Preventing emotional destabilization
- ‚úÖ Supporting human emotional wellbeing
- ‚úÖ Creating stable, trustworthy interactions

